OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy bills to rise more  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fthan predicted, says Ofgem 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fboss                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Domestic energy bills will rise faster 
OL,6, this winter than previously forecast by
OL,7, the energy regulator Ofgem, its chief  
OL,8, executive has admitted to MPs.         
OL,10,FJonathan Brearley said in late May that
OL,11,Fa typical household would pay #800 a   
OL,12,Fyear more from October.                
OL,14,FBut, while giving evidence to MPs, he  
OL,15,Fsaid it was "clear" that estimate for  
OL,16,Fwinter bills now looked too low.       
OL,18,FThe original figure was used by        
OL,19,Fministers when deciding how much to pay
OL,20,Fin direct assistance this winter.      
